<item>
            <title>[LU-11874] conf_param brw_size seems broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11874</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;No big deal but I just noticed that:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;lctl conf_param fsname-OST*.obdfilter.brw_size=16
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;from the Lustre manual, seems broken. It doesn&apos;t change the brw_size values, even after remounting the OSTs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;using&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;echo 16 &amp;gt; /proc/fs/lustre/obdfilter/*${ost}*/brw_size
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;lctl set_param obdfilter.fir-OST*.brw_size=16
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;just works fine to change the values temporarily. We use tuning.conf from shine which is applied at mount time so it doesn&apos;t really affect us but it might affect others. This is with 2.12.0.&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
