                            <comment id="240351" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 18 Jan 2019 18:45:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yep. If&#160; you want to use wildcards you need to use lctl set_param -P obdfilter.*.brw_size=16.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
